title: Nielsen Report,  Percentage of households least prepared for Digital Conversion, USA, June 2009
name: Nielsen Report,  Percentage of households least prepared for Digital Conversion, USA, June 2009
description:
The nation makes a switch from anlog to digital TV today. Nielsen has released a list that shows percent of households by TV market areas that will not receive the new DTV signal! 

According to one report nearly 2.8 million households will be affected by this switch. 

The data was scraped from a jpg image of the list released by Nielsen and then geocoded using DMA shapefiles.
